<DOCNO>WT20-B02-31</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA059-000325-B026-17</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://nesihp01.iaea.or.at:80/worldatom/inforesource/bulletin/bull381/barley.htm 193.81.60.210 19970115011557 text/html 7014
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
