<BODY bgcolor=#ffffff>
<H2>
Cooperation with International Organizations
</H2>
<P>
<HR>
<P>
Fig. 13: Monthly composite samples of rain and snow are collected
at stations around the world and analysed for <SUP>18</SUP>O,
<SUP>2</SUP>H and <SUP>3</SUP>H.  The Agency's laboratory in
Vienna performs part of the analyses of the large numbers of
samples while the remainder are analyzed in Member States. 
(Figure insert shows the relationship of <SUP>18</SUP>O and
<SUP>2</SUP>H in precipitation worldwide, on which interpretation
of hydrological processes are based).
<P>
