<P>
<DL>
<DD> (a) For an advance or advances to the Working Capital Fund, in accordance with Financial Regulation 7.04; and
<P>         
<DD>(b) For a contribution or contributions towards the Agency's Regular Budget, in accordance with the principles the Conference has established for that purpose.
</DL>
</OL>
