<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>
The General Conference
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<CENTER>
<H1>THE IAEA GENERAL CONFERENCE<BR>
<FONT SIZE=-1>
39TH REGULAR SESSION, 18-22 SEPTEMBER 1995<BR>
AUSTRIA CENTER, VIENNA, AUSTRIA</H1>
</FONT>
<HR SIZE=3>
<H2>Advance Information for Delegations</H2>
</CENTER>
<P>
<DL>         
<DD><IMG SRC=/worldatom/images/triblue.gif align=bottom>
<A HREF=#item1>Opening of the Thirty-Ninth Regular Session</A>
<DD><IMG SRC=/worldatom/images/triblue.gif align=bottom>
