<DOCHDR>
http://nesihp01.iaea.or.at:80/GC/statement/outgc.html 193.81.60.210 19970115022113 text/html 6150
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Wed, 15 Jan 1997 02:21:14 GMT
