<DOCNO>WT20-B02-162</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA059-000327-B010-212</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://nesihp01.iaea.or.at:80/worldatom/publications/yearbook/partd.html 193.81.60.210 19970115023344 text/html 1287
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Wed, 15 Jan 1997 02:33:52 GMT
Server: NCSA/1.4
