<HEAD>

<TITLE>CD-ROM</TITLE>

<META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Internet Assistant for Word 1.0Z">
<META NAME="AUTHOR" CONTENT="Stanik Zsolt">
</HEAD>

<BODY>

<P>
<CENTER><A HREF="../products.htm"><IMG SRC="../../graphic/prodserv.gif" BORDER=0></A></CENTER>
<BR>
<BR>

<BLOCKQUOTE>
 <FONT SIZE=6>CD-ROM</FONT> <BR>
<BR>
<BR>
Bibliographic citations included in the INIS Database are available
on CD-ROM from several sources (see <A HREF="../../whatsnew/factcdro.htm">Fact Sheet: INIS Database On CD-ROM</A>
for more information).<BR>
<BR>

</BLOCKQUOTE>

<BLOCKQUOTE>
 <B>INIS DATABASE ON CD-ROM<IMG SRC="../../graphic/1disk13.gif" WIDTH=256 HEIGHT=171 BORDER=0 ALIGN=right>
<BR>
</B>
</BLOCKQUOTE>

<BLOCKQUOTE>
The INIS Database on CD-ROM contains records from 1976 to the
present and is updated quarterly. The full set consists of five
archival disks covering 1976 through 1992 and a current disk covering
1992 to the present. Member States and cooperating international
organizations are licensed to receive a free subscription to the
INIS CD-ROM. Requests for paid subscriptions of the INIS CD-ROM
should be sent to the appropriate regional <A HREF="../silver.htm">SilverPlatter Office</A>
which is the publisher of this product. Information about the
region your country belongs to can be obtained from your national
<A HREF="../../liaison/liaison.htm">INIS Liaison Officer</A> .
<BR>

</BLOCKQUOTE>

<BLOCKQUOTE>
<B>ENERGY SCIENCE AND TECHNOLOGY DATABASE ON CD-ROM<BR>
</B>
</BLOCKQUOTE>

<BLOCKQUOTE>
The United States Energy Science and Technology Database on CD-ROM
(of which INIS is a subset) includes approximately three million
bibliographic records for reports, conferences, journals, patents,
etc. from world-wide sources and covers the time period from 1974
to the present, with abstracts for records from 1976 to the present.
The Energy Science and Technology Database is available through
Knight-Ridder Information Inc. (formerly DIALOG Service). Requests
for this Database on CD-ROM should be directed to <A HREF="../knight.htm">Knight Ridder Office</A>
</BLOCKQUOTE>

<BLOCKQUOTE>
<B>ETDE ENERGY DATABASE ON CD-ROM<BR>
</B>
</BLOCKQUOTE>

<BLOCKQUOTE>
INIS data are available also from the ETDE Energy Database which
includes all of the INIS Database. It covers the period from 1987
to the present and is updated quarterly. The full set consists
of five archival disks and one current disk. Requests for the
ETDE Energy Database on CD-ROM should be directed to the appropriate
<A HREF="../silver.htm">SilverPlatter Office</A> which is the
publisher of this product. Geographic restrictions may apply.
Click <A HREF="http://apollo.osti.gov/summit/focus/osti_etd.html">here</A>
for more information on the Energy Technology Data Exchange (ETDE)
Program. <BR>
<BR>

</BLOCKQUOTE>

