<HR SIZE=1 NOSHADE>
<CENTER><H3>Joint Protocol Relating to the Application of the
Vienna Convention and the Paris Convention
<BR>
Signature, ratification, acceptance, approval or accession
<BR>
Status as of 31 December 1995</H3>
</CENTER>
<P>
<TABLE BORDER=0 WIDTH=100%>
<TR>
<TH VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT>State</TH><TH VALIGN=TOP
ALIGN=LEFT>Date of
Signature</TH><TH VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT>Means and date of
expression<BR>of consent to be bound</TH><TH VALIGN=TOP
ALIGN=LEFT>Entry into Force</TH></TR>
<TR>
<TD COLSPAN=4><HR NOSHADE SIZE=1></TD>
</TR>
<TR>
<TD VALIGN=TOP>Argentina</TD>
<TD VALIGN=TOP>21 Sept. 1988</TD>
