<P>
<I>(P) indicates Party to Paris Convention
<BR>
(V) indicates Party to Vienna Convention
<BR>
<SUP>1/</SUP> does not include the Faroe Islands
<BR>
<SUP>2/</SUP> for the Kingdom in Europe
</I>
<P>The Joint Protocol entered into force on 27 April 1992, i.e.
three months after the date of deposit of instruments of
ratification, acceptance, approval or accession by at least five
States Party to the Vienna Convention and five States Party to
the Paris Convention.
