<CENTER><H3>Agreement on the Privileges and Immunities of the
Agency</H3>
<B>Acceptances by Member States</B>
</CENTER>
<P>
<OL>
<LI>The list of Member States shows the 65 Members which, by 30
September 1995, had accepted the Agreement on the Privileges
and Immunities of the International Atomic Energy Agency, as
provided for in Section 38 thereof.
<P>
<LI>The list is followed by the texts of reservations made to the
Agreement.
</OL>
<P>
<I>(Note:  This Addendum brings up to date, and hence
supersedes, Addendum 9.)</I>
