<HEAD>

<TITLE>Magnetic Media</TITLE>

<META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Internet Assistant for Word 1.0Z">
<META NAME="AUTHOR" CONTENT="Stanik Zsolt">
</HEAD>

<BODY>

<P>
<CENTER><A HREF="../products.htm"><IMG SRC="../../graphic/prodserv.gif" BORDER=0></A></CENTER>
<BR>
<BR>

<BLOCKQUOTE>
 <FONT SIZE=6>Magnetic Media</FONT> <BR>
<BR>
<BR>
<IMG SRC="../../graphic/1disk51.gif" WIDTH=250 HEIGHT=166 BORDER=0 ALIGN=right>
The INIS Magnetic Media Service provides current or back issues
of magnetic tapes or cartridges containing the checked and processed
input data. Current media are shipped monthly (two issues) or
semi-monthly (one issue) as requested by the INIS Liaison Officer.
Back issues are provided upon special request. For more detailed
information on this service see the <A HREF="../../whatsnew/fact995.htm">Fact Sheet - INIS Database and Authorities on Magnetic Media</A>
. Requests for INIS magnetic media should be sent through the
<A HREF="../../liaison/liaison.htm">INIS Liaison Officer</A> to
the INIS Secretariat of the IAEA in Vienna, Austria. <BR>
<BR>

</BLOCKQUOTE>

