alt="General Info on Waste Management" align="bottom" width="531"
height="133"> </p>
<p>Keep America Beautiful, Inc. provides information on the
options for safely handling municipal solid waste, as well as for
litter prevention and beautification. Please check back
occasionally to see new publications as they are released. </p>
<hr>
<h3>Integrated Solid Waste Management</h3>
<dl>
    <dt><a href="mswfact.html"><em>Focus Fact Sheet: Integrated
        Solid Waste Management</em></a><br>
    </dt>
    <dd>explains integrated solid waste management, and gives a
        brief description of the options available.</dd>
    <dd>&#160;</dd>
    <dt><a href="overview.html"><em>Overview of Integrated Waste
        Management</em></a><br>
    </dt>
    <dd>provides a broad overview of options currently available
        for disposing of solid waste. </dd>
</dl>
<hr>
<h3>Recycling</h3>
<p><strong>Brochures:</strong> </p>
<dl>
    <dd>&#160;</dd>
    <dt><a href="cycle.html"><em>Completing the Recycling Cycle</em></a><br>
    </dt>
    <dd>provides tips on buying recycled products to complete the
        &quot;recycling cycle.&quot; </dd>
    <dd>&#160;</dd>
    <dt><a href="fridge.html"><em>Appliance Recycling</em></a><br>
    </dt>
    <dd>explains the proper way to dispose of old appliances. </dd>
    <dd>&#160;</dd>
    <dt><a href="tires.html"><em>Focus Fact Sheet: Tire Recovery</em></a><br>
    </dt>
    <dd>explains what can be done with recovered tires. 
        <p><br>
        </p>
    </dd>
    <dt><strong>KAB's Comprehensive Recycling Study</strong></dt>
    <dd>&#160;</dd>
    <dt><a href="study.html">Executive Summary of <em>The Role of
        Recycling in Integrated Solid Waste Management to the
        Year 2000</em></a><br>
    </dt>
    <dd>by Franklin Associates, Ltd. provides a very brief (2
        pages) overview of the results from the comprehensive
        study on recycling and solid waste; for full summary, see
        below. </dd>
    <dd>&#160;</dd>
    <dt><a href="stdy-ful.html">Summary of <em>The Role of
        Recycling in Integrated Solid Waste Management to the
        Year 2000</em></a><br>
    </dt>
    <dd>by Franklin Associates, Ltd. provides a more
        comprehensive (24 pages) overview of the results from the
        comprehensive study on recycling and solid waste. <br>
    </dd>
</dl>
<hr>
<h3>Composting</h3>
<dl>
    <dt><a href="compost.html"><em>Backyard Composting</em></a><br>
    </dt>
    <dd>explains how composting works, and how to set up your own
        back yard composting pile.</dd>
</dl>
<hr>
<h3>Litter, Beautification, Public Lands</h3>
<dl>
    <dt><a href="cleanup.html"><em>Community Cleanup</em></a> <br>
    </dt>
    <dd>helps you plan your cleanup and ensure the site you've
        cleaned <em>stays</em> clean.</dd>
    <dd>&#160;</dd>
    <dt><a href="water.html"><em>Marine Litter Prevention</em></a><br>
    </dt>
    <dd>provides tips for preventing marine litter.</dd>
    <dd>&#160;</dd>
    <dt><a href="tca.html"><em>Take Care of America</em></a> <br>
    </dt>
    <dd>discusses public lands and their care.</dd>
</dl>
<dl>
    <dt><a href="tips.html"><em>Tips for Preventing Litter</em></a> <br>
    </dt>
    <dd>explains why people litter, and provides suggestions for
        preventing it from happening.</dd>
</dl>
