<h3>News &amp; Notes</h3>
<blockquote>
    <p>The 1996 <a href="awn96.html">Award Winning News</a> has
    been released, and its contents can be viewed on this site.
    This newspaper highlights the programs of many 1996 KAB
    National Award and 1996 KAB SYSTEM Award winners.<br>
    </p>
    <p>The <a href="natwin96.html">1996 KAB National Award
    Winners</a> were announced on October 10, 1996. For
    additional information about The KAB National Awards Program
    and other awards programs available, please see our <a
    href="awards.html">Awards</a> page. <br>
    </p>
    <p>The <a href="syswin96.html">1996 KAB SYSTEM Award Winners</a>
    were also announced on October 10, 1996 <em>(the KAB SYSTEM
    awards are open to KAB Certified Affiliates only)</em>. <br>
    </p>
    <p>You may hear &quot;Keep America Beautiful,&quot; the
    official song of Keep America Beautiful, Inc. by visiting our <a
    href="stuff.html#song">Catalog</a>. </p>
</blockquote>
