        What Can We Do With It?</strong><br>
        </a></dt>
    <dd><a name="poster">Full-color poster depicts options for
        managing waste. Five activities (integrated waste
        management, source reduction, composting, sanitary
        landfilling and waste-to-energy) on back of poster, ideal
