<h3><a name="poster">Public Lands Stewardship</a> </h3>
<dl>
    <dt><a href="tca.html"><strong>Take Care of America</strong></a><br>
    </dt>
    <dd>Brochure explains what public lands are and how you can
        help protect them. <em>First copy free, additional copies
        20&#162; each.</em></dd>
</dl>
