</head>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
<p><!--Source code written by Dawn Rosner. FrontPage required for upload, and has tampered with the original coding--></p>
<p><img src="banner9.gif" lowsrc="lbannr9.gif"
alt="KEEP AMERICA BEAUTIFUL, INC." align="bottom" width="531"
height="133"> <br>
<em><strong>WELCOME!</strong></em><em> Keep America Beautiful,
Inc. is a national, non-profit, public education organization
with local affiliates, dedicated to preserving the natural beauty
and environment in American communities and improving waste
handling practices at the community level. Join with us in </em><em><strong>Keeping
America Beautiful one community at a time!</strong></em></p>
<p><br>
<br>
</p>
