<DOCHDR>
http://www.kab.org:80/mswfact.html 204.127.239.150 19970107014303 text/html 7485
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.1
Date: Tuesday, 07-Jan-97 01:46:47 GMT
